		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/db70276619a06b302ebcc35f1ecf47682.png"></span>
				<span>Charge Blade</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>When wielding an axe:<br>completely fills the user's swordmaster gauge.<br><br>When swapped to dual swords:<br>activates a variant of this skill called<br>Crimson Rush. Crimson Rush deals damage<br>to enemies in a line and inflicts scorchrend.<br>If this skill is used directly after Azure Raid,<br>a variant called Double Flame will be used<br>instead. Double Flame deals damage to<br>enemies in a line, reduces their defense,<br>and inflicts scorchrend.</div><div class="skill-detail"><color=#00008B>When Wielding an Axe:</color><br>Skill Energy Required: 10,450<br><br><color=#00008B>When Swapped to Dual Swords:</color><br>Damage: 405 × 4 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,240<br>Special Effects:<br>・Scorchrend<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:</color><br>Damage: 584 × 4 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,240<br>Special Effects:<br>・Defense -5%<br>　　Lasts 10 seconds<br>　　Potency: 5%<br>　　Does not stack<br>・Scorchrend<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6</div></dd><dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b8bc4d0fe334e827bb7fae18c5ca21d62.png"></span>
				<span>Counter Fang</span>
				<div class="skill-cost">
					<span>Shareable</span>
					<div class="txt-num">
						<span>6</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>When wielding an axe:<br>the user temporarily assumes a counter stance,<br>during which they are immune to knockback.<br>If the user is hit by an attack while in this<br>stance, this skill will deal damage to surrounding<br>enemies, dispel one buff from each target,<br>restore half of the damage taken while using<br>this skill as HP, and immediately ready the<br>Charge Blade skill for use. If the user is not hit<br>by an attack while in this skill's counter stance,<br>it will be immediately readied for use again.<br>Some attacks cannot be countered with this skill,<br>and being energized will not upgrade this skill.<br><br>When swapped to dual swords:<br>activates a variant of this skill called Azure Raid.<br>Azure Raid deals damage to surrounding enemies<br>and dispels one buff from each target.<br>If this skill is used directly after Crimson Rush,<br>a variant called Dual Demolition will be used<br>instead. Dual Demolition deals damage to<br>surrounding enemies and dispels one buff from<br>each target.</div><div class="skill-detail"><color=#00008B>When Wielding an Axe:</color><br>Damage: 418 × 6 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 3,120<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>・50% Damage Reduction<br>　　Does not stack<br><br><color=#00008B>When Swapped to Dual Swords:</color><br>Damage: 254 × 7 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,240<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:</color><br>Damage: 421 × 8 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,240<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 12,544<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs</div></dd></dl></div>
