				<span>Blazing Strike</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts scorchrend. Enemies in break state<br>take reduced damage. If the user is targeting<br>an enemy and not using a skill when their<br>remaining shapeshift time runs out, this skill<br>will be used automatically, regardless of<br>whether or not the skill gauge is filled.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 1,078 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 1,470 × 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>・Scorchrend<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・75% against enemies in break state<br></div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
